<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <script>
        (()=>{
            window.history.forward();
        })();
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <center>
        <h2>Example showing the concept of Session in ExpressJS</h2>
    </center>
    <%if(email==""){%>    
    <hr>
    <a href="/">Home</a>    |   
    <a href="/">Login</a>
    <hr>
    <h2>Login Page</h2>
    <%=message%>
    <h2>Get Method</h2>
    <form action="/viewInfo" method="get">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Enter Email" name="email" id="email"> <br>
        <input type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" name="password" id="password"> <br>
        <input type="submit" value="Submit"> 
        <input type="reset" value="Reset"> 
        <br>
    </form>
    <h2>Post Method</h2>
    <form action="/viewInfo" method="post">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Enter Email" name="email" id="email"> <br>
        <input type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" name="password" id="password"> <br>
        <input type="submit" value="Submit"> 
        <input type="reset" value="Reset"> 
        <br>
    </form>

    <%}else{%>
        <hr>
        Welcome <%=email%>  |
        <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
        <hr>
        <h2>Profile Page</h2>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus repellat odio optio, et impedit esse itaque minus. Odit necessitatibus quos repellat voluptatibus veniam quas architecto quasi laborum eaque voluptates maxime ducimus amet autem veritatis cumque error dicta iste, quo reprehenderit fugit velit. Repellendus aspernatur quod dolor voluptas consequuntur! Non, laboriosam?</p>
    <%}%>
</body>
</html>